name: Walter the Rabbit
description:
Welcome to the mystical, magical world of **Walter the Rabbit** NFTs. 

-100% [hand drawn](https://waltertherabbit.com/drawnNotMade.png) by a real human artist. 

-No generative AI sh!*t here. 

Countless non-repetitive characters.  
Surprising stories and locations all over the universe that will amaze and confuse humans and others alike! You can collect, compose and combine some of this NFTs to create epic scenes from the upcoming video game. 

This collection is the first foundational step towards emancipating an artist and creating an awesome video game!
